	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=70265><span id= >Odibil</span></a><br><span id=notbold>7 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good [3.66]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Effect: Everfount <br>Type: Triggered <br>Charges: Unlimited <br><br>Right-clickable effects are considered "Triggered"<br>Whereas procs would be listed as "Random" effects.<br><br>Also, class specific items usually cannot be used by other classes (effect-wise). Only those items which can be right-clicked from the general inventory slot can be used by any class. I'm pretty sure this earring has to be worn for the effect, which would make it mage only.<br><br>Hope that clears it up :)</p>&nbsp;<br><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Odibil Lauxes<br>Magician<br>The Seventh Hammer</td></tr>
